item.title: Artisanal software
item.description: I don’t listen to many podcasts. My interests, even when taking my ADHD medication, tend to flit and bounce with the trajectory of a dust mote in a wind funnel. And so I haven’t really been interested in many topics long enough to develop a habit of listening to podcasts about them.
